    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;The Static Context Header Compression (SCHC) and fragmentation specification (RFC 8724) describes a generic framework for application header compression and fragmentation modes designed for Low-Power Wide Area Network (LPWAN) technologies.  This document defines a profile of SCHC over Sigfox LPWAN and provides optimal parameter values and modes of operation.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
